    <item>
      <title>尽管有停火协议，内塔尼亚胡仍誓言继续与真主党作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/netanyahu-vows-to-keep-fighting-hezbollah-despite-cease-fire-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡誓言将继续打击黎巴嫩真主党，这使人们对国际社会推动停战的前景产生了新的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/netanyahu-vows-to-keep-fighting-hezbollah-despite-cease-fire-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:28:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安哥拉认为拜登即将访问将促进投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/angola-sees-biden-s-upcoming-visit-giving-investment-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉希望美国总统乔·拜登下个月的访问将有助于增加外国投资，因为该国正试图实现经济多元化，摆脱对石油的依赖，减少对中国资本的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/angola-sees-biden-s-upcoming-visit-giving-investment-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新一轮石油危机引发哥伦比亚货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/fresh-bout-of-petro-risk-sparks-rout-in-colombia-s-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在古斯塔沃·佩特罗任职的大部分时间里，哥伦比亚的利率一直很高，以至于外国投资者不得不忍受偶尔出现的政治动荡，而这种动荡通常会吓跑他们。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/fresh-bout-of-petro-risk-sparks-rout-in-colombia-s-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:29:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
